The game layout should be maintained on all pages.
The game should follow a single page app feel.
The landing page should allow a user to login using a discord account or a gmail account.
The landing page should be a single form for login and a top of the page banner for the game.
After logging in, the page should consist of a header banner and a 2 pane layout with a smaller left pane for navigation and a larger right pane for the main game actions.
The game should have a dark color scheme by default - dark greys and light teal accents. Main text can be white or very light grey. the font should be a generic sans serif for legitibility.

Links in the left nav should include:
- Home
- Armory
- Temple
- Training Grounds
- Tepke Mines

Other links will appear in this list, but are not "unlocked" by default.